<item>
            <title>[HBASE-13167] The check for balancerCutoffTime is buggy</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-13167</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In HMaster, the checking logic for balancerCutoffTime in buggy.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;See the following code:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-style: solid;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeHeader panelHeader&quot; style=&quot;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-style: solid;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;HMaster.java&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
1419   &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;private&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; getBalancerCutoffTime() {
1420     &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; balancerCutoffTime =
1421       getConfiguration().getInt(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;hbase.balancer.max.balancing&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, -1);
1422     &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (balancerCutoffTime == -1) {
1423       &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// No time period set so create one
&lt;/span&gt;1424       &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; balancerPeriod =
1425         getConfiguration().getInt(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;hbase.balancer.period&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, 300000);
1426       balancerCutoffTime = balancerPeriod;
1427       &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// If nonsense period, set it to balancerPeriod
&lt;/span&gt;1428       &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (balancerCutoffTime &amp;lt;= 0) balancerCutoffTime = balancerPeriod;
1429     }
1430     &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; balancerCutoffTime;
1431   }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Basically, the check for &quot;nonsense period&quot; is no effect, because  balancerCutoffTime is always assigned to be balancerPeriod whatever the value is. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
