                            <comment id="14353902" author="mantonov" created="Mon, 9 Mar 2015 23:47:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Trivial patch.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A note..if max cutoff time isn&apos;t set, we&apos;re currently defaulting to period time. I sort of remember it used to be defaulted to half of balancer period time (2.5 min by default). Do we want to stick with cutoff time == period time behavior?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
