                            <comment id="14355318" author="apurtell" created="Tue, 10 Mar 2015 17:57:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;lgtm if we want to stay with the current behavior. (Sounds reasonable to me.)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14355715" author="mantonov" created="Tue, 10 Mar 2015 21:07:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=apurtell&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;apurtell&quot;&gt;Andrew Purtell&lt;/a&gt;. It might be more conservative to limit max cutoff time to about 0.75 of period time, but current behavior sounds reasonable.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
